  "Talisman of Five Elements": { id: 5423, label: "Talismã dos Elementos", description: "Talismã dos Elementos\nMAX Lv : 5\n^777777Skill requirement : Talisman Mastery 1^000000\nSkill form : ^993300Active^000000\nType : ^777777Buff^000000\nTarget : ^777777Single Target^000000\nDetails : ^777777Consumes 5 Soul Talismans.\nAttaches the talisman of five elements to self or 1 party member to increases physical and magical damage against water, wind, earth, fire and neutral property enemies.\nCan only be used on target who equips weapon.^000000\n^ffffff_^000000\n[Lv 1]: ^777777Damage bonus +4%/Duration: 180 sec^000000\n[Lv 2]: ^777777Damage bonus +8%/Duration: 210 sec^000000\n[Lv 3]: ^777777Damage bonus +12%/Duration: 240 sec^000000\n[Lv 4]: ^777777Damage bonus +16%/Duration: 270 sec^000000\n[Lv 5]: ^777777Damage bonus +20%/Duration: 300 sec^000000" },
  "Totem of Tutelary": { id: 5422, label: "Totem de Tutela", description: "Totem de Tutela\nMAX Lv : 5\n^777777Skill requirement : Talisman Mastery 3, Soul Mastery 3^000000\nSkill form : ^993300Active^000000\nType : ^777777Recovery^000000\nTarget : ^7777771 cell ground target^000000\nDetails : ^777777Consumes 10 Soul Talismans.\nSummons the Totem of Tutelary which worships the guardian deity on ground to recover HP and SP of nearby party members including the user at certain interval.\nRecovers additional amount depends on level of Talisman Mastery user learned, user's base level and CRT.^000000\n^ffffff_^000000\n[Lv 1] : ^777777HP recovery amount :1000+(Talisman Mastery Lv x50)\nSP recovery : 50+(Talisman Mastery Lv x5)/AOE: 5x5 cells^000000\n[Lv 2] : ^777777HP recovery amount :1500+(Talisman Mastery Lv x100)\nSP recovery : 100+(Talisman Mastery Lv x10)/AOE: 5x5 cells^000000\n[Lv 3] : ^777777HP recovery amount :2000+(Talisman Mastery Lv x150)\nSP recovery : 150+(Talisman Mastery Lv x15)/AOE: 7x7 cells^000000\n[Lv 4] : ^777777HP recovery amount :2500+(Talisman Mastery Lv x200)\nSP recovery : 200+(Talisman Mastery Lv x20)/AOE: 7x7 cells^000000\n[Lv 5] : ^777777HP recovery amount :3000+(Talisman Mastery Lv x250)\nSP recovery : 250+(Talisman Mastery Lv x25)/AOE: 9x9 cells^000000" },
