  "All in the Sky": { id: 5474, label: "Firmamento", description: "Firmamento\nMAX Lv : 10\n^777777Skill requirement : War Book Mastery 5, Rising Sun 1, Rising Moon 1^000000\nSkill form : ^993300Active^000000\nType : ^777777Melee Physical^000000\nTarget : ^777777Single Target^000000\nConsumes : ^FF0000AP 100^000000\nDetails : ^777777Accumulates all of celestial energy into the user's feet then dashes to the target and kicks it with all might,\ninflicts melee physical damage to the target. If the target is player. Drains its AP to 0,\nif the target is demihuman or demon race monster, the skill deals damage for 3 hits.\nDeals additional damage depends on user's base level and POW.\nHas a chance to trigger critical, critical chance is the user's Cri.\nThe effectiveness of critical modifier is applied by half.^000000\n^ffffff_^000000\n[Lv 1] : ^777777ATK 2000%^000000\n[Lv 2] : ^777777ATK 4000%^000000\n[Lv 3] : ^777777ATK 6000%^000000\n[Lv 4] : ^777777ATK 8000%^000000\n[Lv 5] : ^777777ATK 10000%^000000\n[Lv 6] : ^777777ATK 12000%^000000\n[Lv 7] : ^777777ATK 14000%^000000\n[Lv 8] : ^777777ATK 16000%^000000\n[Lv 9] : ^777777ATK 18000%^000000\n[Lv10] : ^777777ATK 20000%^000000" },
  "Dark Dragon - Nightmare": { id: 5495, label: "Mahou do Pesadelo", description: "Mahou do Pesadelo\nMAX Lv : 1\n^777777Skill requirement : Mirage 1, Red Flame Cannon 5, Cold Blooded Cannon 5, Thundering Cannon 5, Golden Dragon Cannon 5, Darkening Cannon 5^000000\nSkill form : ^3F0099Active(AP)^000000\nType : ^777777Magic^000000\nTarget : ^777777Instant Cast^000000\nConsumes : ^FF0000AP 30^000000\nDetails: ^777777Summons a shadow dragon in an 11x11 cell area around you and inflicts powerful dark magic damage.\nAdditional fire property magic damage of the same power is inflicted to the target affected by the nightmare effect (the nightmare effect is canceled).\nDamage is additionally increased depending on the caster's base level and SPL.^000000\n^ffffff_^000000\n[Lv 1] : ^777777MATK 12000%^000000" },
