  "Mission Bombard": { id: 5415, label: "Bombardeio", description: "Bombardeio\nMAX Lv : 10\n^777777Skill requirement : Grenade Mastery 5, Grenades Dropping 3^000000\nSkill form : ^3F0099Active(AP)^000000\nType : ^777777Range Physical^000000\nTarget : ^7777771 cell ground target^000000\nConsumes : ^FF0000AP 100^000000\nDetails: ^777777 Drops a large bomb with an explosive power of 9x9 cells on 1 cell of the ground, and continuously drops 3 small bombs with an explosive power of 5x5 cells within the range once every 0.25 seconds for 10 seconds, causing long range physical damage.\nDamage is additionally increased depending on the Grenade Mastery skill level, caster's base level, and CON.^000000\n^ffffff_^000000\n[Lv 1] : ^777777ATK 6000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 1000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 2] : ^777777ATK 7000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 1200+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 3] : ^777777ATK 8000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 1400+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 4] : ^777777ATK 9000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 1600+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 5] : ^777777ATK 10000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 1800+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 6] : ^777777ATK 11000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 2000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 7] : ^777777ATK 12000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 2200+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 8] : ^777777ATK 13000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 2400+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv 9] : ^777777ATK 14000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 2600+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000\n[Lv10] : ^777777ATK 15000+(Grenade Mastery Lv x100)%\nPer hit ATK 2800+(Grenade Mastery Lv x30)%^000000" },
  "Moon Slasher": { id: 2320, label: "Espiral Lunar", description: "Espiral Lunar ^777777(Moon Slasher)^000000\nNível máximo: ^7777775^000000\nPré-requisitos: ^777777Perícia com Lança 1^000000\nTipo: ^777777Ofensiva^000000\nDescrição:\n^008080Apenas com Lança.^000000\n^777777Causa dano físico corpo a corpo na área de\n7x7 células ao redor do usuário. O dano é\nafetado pelo nível de base e pelo nível de\nLança do Destino. Após o uso, aumenta o\ndano causado por Lança do Destino.^000000\nNível l ATQ l Duração do bônus\n[Nv 1]: ^777777120%^000000 l ^7777772 segundos^000000\n[Nv 2]: ^777777240%^000000 l ^7777774 segundos^000000\n[Nv 3]: ^777777360%^000000 l ^7777776 segundos^000000\n[Nv 4]: ^777777480%^000000 l ^7777778 segundos^000000\n[Nv 5]: ^777777600%^000000 l ^77777710 segundos^000000" },
